CodeSharp is a small CMS based on CodeIgniter.

Currently in Alpha version. You can download a version here: https://github.com/downloads/TCotton/CodeSharp/codesharp-beta.zip

1. Create the database and include the database details in file application/config/database.php

2. Change the $config['base_url'] value to your domain name in application/config/config.php

3. Run install file : http://www.example.com/index.php/install.php

4. Enter values requested

This will install a full version of CodeSharp

Afterwards, change the error level in the main index file to production if coding work is to continue

[At the moment there is a hack installation method. This will change in a forthcoming version]
